1555337568","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"在开发的过程中还是以实现功能为第一目标，再完成功能以后会对这些部分已经优化，看看能不能能够改进的地方","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":86131,"user_name":"旺旺","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1213887,"ip_address":"","ucode":"161B267F67EBCA","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/12/85/bf/5c5e86bb.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555312732,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555312732","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"在没钱的时候，绩效优先；在已盈利或已确定将来必定盈利的时候，考虑两者折中。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":86041,"user_name":"Y","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1488762,"ip_address":"","ucode":"940567CFFE11B3","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/b7/7a/26df9a6d.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555304490,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555304490","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"需要让有决定权的人有这样的思维或者自己成为有决定权的人","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":85762,"user_name":"小优","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1467257,"ip_address":"","ucode":"08D3224FFAF722","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/63/79/4fa91b0f.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555226287,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555226287","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"我的理解是，增长不只是用户量上的增长，质量也很重要，像大客户这种用户，量是很有限的，持续提高服务和优化产品或系统，才能持续发展！互联网用户也是一样，留存才能增值！","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":85527,"user_name":"赵亚洲","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1171858,"ip_address":"","ucode":"0C89D2AC1D445F","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/11/e1/92/cdd1800a.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555113592,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555113592","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"KPI和创新的冲突有一种典型的表现形式：领导者既规定了最终目标，又规定了实现目标的路径，而规定路径往往来自领导者过去的成功经验，不一定适应新的问题。<br>对领导者来说，学会看结果和授权也许能解决一部分冲突问题。<br>对执行者来说，在完成规定事项的基础上，尽可能做出一些详尽、靠谱的计划并完成汇报，也许是问题的另一半解决方案。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":85456,"user_name":"流萤","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1336453,"ip_address":"","ucode":"849E83E17DB7D6","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/14/64/85/3cd049a2.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555063633,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555063633","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"去分析流失的和未流失的用户的差异点，可以做用户的留存；去分析来了使用了产品和未使用产品的差异点，可以做用户激活?<br>创新还是有些难，可能数据驱动更能很好的传播吧！但是其实很多公司也都做了这些事情，可能还是没有发现突破点，这种怎呢办呢？","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":85438,"user_name":"尚武","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1490069,"ip_address":"","ucode":"2CB2B841E98AFF","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/bc/95/84ec6c17.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555060353,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555060353","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"如果像是电商的话，着陆页也是增长的一部分，一个好的着陆页能带来高转化。老师可以讲一下如何做一个优秀的着陆页。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":85433,"user_name":"桃园悠然在","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1017637,"ip_address":"","ucode":"704460D9CAD1CB","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/87/25/898dea4e.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555059662,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555059662","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"补充一点：差异化洞察真的挺难的，很多洞察是基于对业务的深刻了解，而不是YY出来的，很多分析师角色算不上洞察，而是“制造结论”。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":85429,"user_name":"桃园悠然在","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1017637,"ip_address":"","ucode":"704460D9CAD1CB","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/87/25/898dea4e.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555059440,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555059440","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"我所见到的实际情况是：绩效不可能丢在一边，所谓为过程鼓掌为结果买单。当然，有野心的团队往往有创新的想法、科学的落地方案博得更大的蛋糕（绩效）。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":85416,"user_name":"火腿","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1308116,"ip_address":"","ucode":"40F17DBC18F5D5","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/13/f5/d4/5a0a2f8d.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555055859,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":2,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555055859","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"请教个问题， 租房网站的用户增长， 老师有没有什么好的指引？","like_count":0,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":2826277,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/2b/20/25/1c48ff6c.jpg","nickname":"reverse","note":"","ucode":"746DF4840CF617","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":555978,"discussion_content":"从供应链角度：能提供的房源面积、房源成本、装修风格都是会影响用户转化的重要指标；是否对内容即“房源”做精细化运营；\n从平台产品角度：1. 推荐：首页是否个性化推荐板块，例如有营造租房愉悦感的UGC社区板块（不同收入来源教育背景的用户对内容板块的喜好程度不一，如极简风、温馨风等）2.搜索：是否前端有便于用户快速定位的过滤功能板块，包括自主筛选不同地铁交通路线房源、房源价格、房源属性（包括朝向、面积、户型）、可解释最长通勤时间等；用户需要快速检索快速定位后才可提高交易转化率；","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1647155460,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]},{"author":{"id":1722044,"avatar":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/Q0j4TwGTfTIGGBhiaUAJpeFG1oOcPAvR5JYJhmgxInEe7Z0dcnuSo7tDaq5qr25z8ZaEmVm71onxUMMhsCj5Jcg/132","nickname":"Geek_d5a704","note":"","ucode":"8AD7331848A7C4","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":272416,"discussion_content":"最终为用户，简单而有效","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1590303257,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":85376,"user_name":"Hunter Liu","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1474463,"ip_address":"","ucode":"BD1FD203A295DC","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/7f/9f/ca7b20cd.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555048993,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555048993","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"我是项目管理人员，当前的工作状态肯定是以KPI为主，但也会结合产品的情况和工作量适当加入创新内容，成本占比高的创新通常在一个项目的生命周期内不会被采纳，虽然是平台话的产品，但所谓的创新功能也只是因为别的toB的项目已经实现，并且竞品已经有了，平台化时才想着去实现，并不是做过深入调研得出的结论，这种现象其实是以领导和老客户为中心。开发人员通常会问，你这个功能有数据支撑吗？产品人员通常会被开发人员问得哑口无言。只得说某总已经拍了这个提案，咱们照做就成了。<br><br>而我做项目的痛点是，到底怎样的内容才能算创新？<br>就算是看到了创新点，通常评估出来的工作量和成本项目无法承受，今天老师讲到了小成本实验，希望通过专栏解决这个痛点。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":85373,"user_name":"留青","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1488866,"ip_address":"","ucode":"71D846719F8560","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/b7/e2/af0f769c.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555048343,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555048343","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"作为设计人员，第一反应是要靠转化率。结合上一讲内容，“最终为用户，简单却有效”，创新可以做小版本迭代、AB测试、通过这样的方法做小创新，积累到一定程度后再做大的版本迭代，以数据（用户反应）为根据，做创新。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":85365,"user_name":"Lindm","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1415532,"ip_address":"","ucode":"31292436A81543","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/15/99/6c/f5f4414b.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555046219,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555046219","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"以最小的成本实现价值最大化，洞察以用户为中心的爆破点，实验并实现“增长”。打磨产品，驱动产品增长，带动价值增长，促进企业增长。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":85343,"user_name":"阳","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1489625,"ip_address":"","ucode":"B541B455A9682C","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/ba/d9/23d8b97e.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555040782,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555040782","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"偏向结合，绩效较直接，看数据结果比较直观，创新需要不断测试通过绩效去表现，有点小版本迭代，能快速试错。<br>零售，大数据推送实现千人千面情况下，依旧难把握“猜你喜欢”，但已经有所提升，直播+电商结合很不错，带来的增长很明显。复盘很需要学习~","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":85293,"user_name":"Jim","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1021090,"ip_address":"","ucode":"4E0B06B63A746F","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/94/a2/891520ff.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555031268,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555031268","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"回答：<br>先保证KPI完成，因为这是部门或公司的生存基础。<br>日常工作保证留出时间去探索创新。<br>一旦试验有效，逐渐提高KPI中创新贡献的占比。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":85287,"user_name":"coder","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1136797,"ip_address":"","ucode":"4F9A006DA78074","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/11/58/9d/91d795cf.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555030907,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555030907","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"现在的工作主要还是借鉴，创新方面做的还不多，公司目前刚成立，很多东西还没建立起来，还是用传统的一些手段获客","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":85282,"user_name":"吴小智","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1310798,"ip_address":"","ucode":"C7C9F58B5C9F7B","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/14/00/4e/be2b206b.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555030799,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555030799","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"爱了，老师举的例子太棒了","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":85268,"user_name":"张亚楠","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1189279,"ip_address":"","ucode":"45EF87FA1ACDC6","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/12/25/9f/057b284a.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555029527,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555029527","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"增长黑客，是分析现有数据，满足用户现有需求。<br>产品极客，是利用自身经验和嗅觉，发掘用户潜在的，未来的需求。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":85263,"user_name":"hua168","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1065255,"ip_address":"","ucode":"CFF9A7E86EBA48","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/41/27/3ff1a1d6.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555029058,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555029058","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"做增长是不是要自己亲自去找客户群体调查？<br>像我们都是互联网产品，他是怎么去找用户去调查，还要反馈的？","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":85262,"user_name":"野草","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1447769,"ip_address":"","ucode":"87F14BDC35FC71","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/17/59/1e465966.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555029018,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555029018","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"通过今天的学习，对于用户增长有了新的理解，产品应该有一个核心理念，这个理念一定是以用户为中心，以增长用户价值进而增长商业价值为基本点的，而差异化洞察正是在这一理念的基础上从全局思考得出的创新点，这正是产品极客正在做的。每一个创新即使机会也是挑战，方向正确了就是把握住了机会，如果方向不正确那可能就会影响到整体战略，为了更好把握机会迎接挑战，增长极客的优势就凸显了，既可以通过大数据技术分析初步验证是否大方向正确，又可以先通过技术手段初步试水创新点，如果有效果，再全力投入","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":85252,"user_name":"李沛欣","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1362695,"ip_address":"","ucode":"98874954230D95","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/14/cb/07/e34220d6.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555028436,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555028436","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"看了您的理解突然觉得他们都并没有真的为用户而考虑，前者是放养，后者是圈养，有放有收，一张一弛才是真的符合中庸之道。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":85239,"user_name":"沃斯 亨利baci","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1489569,"ip_address":"","ucode":"6C7FB023A1D4C3","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/ba/a1/e037819a.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555026675,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555026675","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"在绩效和创新之间，如何取舍？<br>这里的绩效，可能是这样：【哇塞那个公司用这个手段，迅速获得巨大成功了，我们也这样】，然而我们不顾自身情况，用了【别人成功的手段】后，就一定也能巨大成功吗？<br>这里的【我们】与【那个公司】不可能完全一样。创新是一种思维，追求与众不同的差异化，通过差异化来达成符合自身的持续【绩效】获取。<br>一个是指标，一个是思维方式，的确如老师所说，可以兼得。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":85231,"user_name":"Jesse","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1005210,"ip_address":"","ucode":"2283CD8C971ADC","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/56/9a/c71d326f.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555024707,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555024707","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"已学习 打卡。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":85201,"user_name":"头发茂密","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1474084,"ip_address":"","ucode":"263C8B685F19A5","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/7e/24/afb15de3.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555000252,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555000252","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"以工作的目的和重要性为尺度<br>如果，工作要求高，十分重要，老大要求尽力保证不出错，那就选择绩效优先，可控范围内小规模创新。<br>如果，工作要求没那么高，能力范围内，允许一定的出错率，那么，可以选择创新有效，其次保证绩效。","like_count":0}]}